              </p>
              <div class="mt-auto">
                <p class="pb-3"><a href="/miami/photos" class="text-gray-600 text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-montserrat font-bold underline">Photos</a> / <a href="/miami" class="text-gray-600 text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-montserrat font-bold underline">Connections</a></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- London Event Card -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 flex flex-col">
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] relative overflow-hidden">
            <%= image_tag "events/london.png", class: "w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-1000" %>
          </div>
          <div class="px-8 pt-8 pb-12 flex flex-col flex-grow">
            <div class="text-center flex flex-col flex-grow">
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-light mb-2 font-austin text-gray-900 tracking-widest">LONDON</h3>
              <div class="w-16 h-px bg-gray-300 mx-auto mb-4"></div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-montserrat mb-2">A Night of Dreams</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs md:text-sm mb-4 max-w-sm mx-auto py-2">
                We had the most wonderful time together, and can't wait to hear what you thought. Drop us a note on our missed connections page and view the pictures from the event.
              </p>
              <div class="mt-auto">

                <p class="pb-3"><a href="/london/photos" class="text-gray-600 text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-montserrat font-bold underline">Photos</a> / <a href="/london" class="text-gray-600 text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-montserrat font-bold underline">Connections</a></p>

              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Paris Event Card -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 flex flex-col">
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] relative overflow-hidden">
            <%= image_tag "events/paris.png", class: "w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-1000" %>
          </div>
          <div class="px-8 pt-8 pb-12 flex flex-col flex-grow">
            <div class="text-center flex flex-col flex-grow">
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-light mb-2 font-austin text-gray-900 tracking-widest">PARIS</h3>
              <div class="w-16 h-px bg-gray-300 mx-auto mb-4"></div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-montserrat mb-2">A Parisian Soirée</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs md:text-sm mb-4 max-w-sm mx-auto py-2">
                A beautiful evening filled with wonderful people and meaningful conversation. Thank you to all who attended and made it a truly special soirée in the city of lights.
              </p>
              <div class="mt-auto">
                <p class="pb-3"><a href="/paris/photos" class="text-gray-600 text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-montserrat font-bold underline">Photos</a> / <a href="/paris" class="text-gray-600 text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-montserrat font-bold underline">Connections</a></p>
